<h1>Andrea Funk</h1>

<h2><a href="/">/now</a>: <a href="http://www.toocooltshirtquilts.com/now">toocooltshirtquilts.com/now</a></h2>

<h2>Location:</h2>
<p>
Charlotte
MI
United States
</p>

<h2>Professional title:</h2>
<p>
T-shirt Quilt Goddess. Founder of Too Cool T-shirt Quilts.
</p>

<h2>What do you do?</h2>
<p>
I tell my customer's stories by transforming their T-shirts in to quilts.
</p>

<h2>Why?</h2>
<p>
I love hearing my customers tears of joy when they see their quilt.
</p>

<h2>Recent thought or epiphany?</h2>
<p>
I live by, "This too will end." Nothing, be it hard or easy will last, so I had better be ready and planning for the next thing.
</p>

<h2>What should we read?</h2>
<p>
Atomic Accidents: A History of Nuclear Meltdowns and Disasters; From the Ozark Mountains to Fukushima by James Mahaffey. Riveting and easy to understand.
</p>

